        ### Events for anything, contextualized

        The API supports any timestamped content, including files. Health metrics, locations, pictures, audio samples, notes, activities, vegetable garden yields, you name it. See [the standard types directory](/event-types).

        Organization is handled via simple and proven constructs like a hierarchical structure (streams) and tags.

